import React, { Component } from "react";
import {
  Col,
  Row,
  Button,
  Form,
  FormGroup,
  Label,
  Input,
  FormText
} from "reactstrap";

class Login extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Form>
        <Row form>
          <Col md={6}>
            <FormGroup>
              <Label for="exampleEmail">Email</Label>
              <Input
                type="email"
                name="email"
                id="exampleEmail"
                placeholder="with a placeholder"
              />
            </FormGroup>
          </Col>
          <Col md={6}>
            <FormGroup>
              <Label for="examplePassword">Password</Label>
              <Input
                type="password"
                name="password"
                id="examplePassword"
                placeholder="password placeholder"
              />
            </FormGroup>
          </Col>
        </Row>

        <Button>Sign in</Button>
      </Form>
    );
  }
}

export default Login;
